WHAT WE REALLY
WANTED TO DO WAS

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:12.000
TO DEVISE SOMETHING

00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:15.000
THAT WOULD LET THE BABIES
DO SOMETHING FOR THEMSELVES.

